//- belongs in the why-section. Same field and cutoff as the Metrics
//- tab's TTFB tile (gwvTtfbClass): 800 ms is where Web Vitals stops
//- calling a TTFB good.
- const whyTtfb = whyTimings && whyTimings.ttfb ? Math.round(whyTimings.ttfb) : undefined
- const ttfbSlow = !!(whyTtfb && whyTtfb >= 800)
//- Reflows are windowed to before the page painted — a reflow between
//- FCP and LCP still delays the largest paint (pages that paint early
//- and then thrash layout would otherwise show nothing here). The
//- window ends at the LATEST known paint milestone (LCP can land
